NAME: Wage employees; Female/male ratio
Explanation: Female/male ratio >1 means more female employees than male employees

NAME: Employers; Female/male ratio
Explanation: >1 means more female employers than male employers

NAME: Wages; Female/male ratio
Explanation: Ratio of estimated female to male earned income

NAME: Vulnerable employment
Explanation: Share of vulnerable employment in total employment (%), women

NAME: GDP percent real change
Explanation: Percentage change in real GDP, over previous year.

NAME: Private consumption percent real change
Explanation: Percentage change in real private consumption, over previous period.

NAME: Gross national savings rate (%)
Explanation: Aggregate national savings by the public and private sector as a percentage of nominal GDP.

NAME: Gross national savings/investment (%)
Explanation: Gross national savings as a percentage of gross domestic investment.
